Auburn Gresham Healthy Lifestyle Hub Grand Opening


Posted on October 26, 2022








            Event Details
          Heading link



 
Copy link






UIC Office of Community Collaboration Neighborhood Centers Initiative invites you as our special guest to the Auburn Gresham Healthy Lifestyle Hub Grand Opening!
When
Friday, November 11, 2020
4:00 to 7:00 p.m.
Where
At 839 W. 79th Street
Chicago, IL 60620
Free of charge and open to the public.
During your visit, join us in the new Auburn Gresham Neighborhood Center, Suite 312, for introductions and light refreshments!
This momentous celebration is organized by the Greater Auburn Gresham Development Corporation.






            Health Care for the Auburn-Gresham Community
          Heading link



 
Copy link






The Auburn-Gresham Healthy Lifestyle Hub is anchored by the UI Health Mile Square Primary and Immediate Care Center, which fills a gap in available care by providing adult and pediatric primary care, women’s health care, pregnancy and prenatal care, behavioral health and substance use disorder care, HIV care, dental care, and preventative care. Pharmacy services are also available onsite.



      Learn More About the Healthy Lifestyle Hub
    






